    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, functional condition and would make a great project car or a basic daily driver for someone looking for value over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear in the driver's seat, though all essential electronics and the air conditioning still work as intended. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car that has served its previous owner well but now shows the typical signs of high mileage and regular use.",
      "price": 19500.0,
