    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, so you won't find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and honestly feels brand new. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 1994 Mazda RX-7, maintained to an exacting standard. The 13B-REW rotary engine delivers linear power via its original sequential twin-turbocharger setup, with recent compression tests yielding optimal results across all rotor faces. This chassis remains structurally rigid, featuring its factory-spec four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for neutral cornering dynamics. Finished in its original paint with a flawless interior, this FD3S retains its legendary 50/50 weight distribution and lightweight aluminum components. A turnkey example for the discerning collector seeking peak mechanical integrity and period-correct performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    }
